      <abstract encodinganalog="5203_">This collection contains letters from
		  customers throughout Montana and nearby states ordering fruit from Theon H.
		  Durnford in Lolo, Montana, 1913-1924 and Durnford's receipts and statements
		  from Hughes Mercantile in Lolo between 1917 and 1919.</abstract>
